cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a deep learning-based approach for visual novelty detection, which is a problem related to computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel loss function and uses transfer learning, which are related to machine learning. Therefore, the other likely categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
